{"tid":1429161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粉嶺警黑大龍鳳","createTime":"2019-08-07T12:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T12:56:40.000Z","uid":109770,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9a32331bbb79f096c2c0e68d7b57a53baea88abb","tid":1429161,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:25:08.000Z","msg":"前兩日粉嶺火車站往蓬瀛仙館方向天橋（粉嶺連儂天橋）有市民比黑社會用鎚同銼襲擊受傷<br />\n然後個黑社會比網民迅速起底<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2TaB3w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2TaB3w.png&h=8d01a583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n突然今日就話今晚九點半有人會入黎粉嶺搞事<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但粉嶺人根本唔知有依件事<br />\n相信係一場警黑大龍鳳<br />\n冇人會出去<br />\n大家亦唔洗入黎中伏<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n資訊：<br />\n上水狗屋（位於粉嶺）突然落閘<br />\n鄰近祥華邨保安亦同住戶講今晚九點半會有人搞事所以將所有垃圾桶收起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bbf0be577e8034149b27297983bdfd072ebc45d","tid":1429161,"uid":109770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:27:08.000Z","msg":"自推十次，沉底由佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e266a19d65d48a188cbd757f4ed298737fdfb34b","tid":1429161,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:27:27.000Z","msg":"自推九次，沉底由佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8f8deec1b244cba9bf94f4b279afdc16c54bd3","tid":1429161,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:27:40.000Z","msg":"自推八次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb459957d211a51b3ce4eb9881e84caffe8eea55","tid":1429161,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:28:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/